"{    \"translations\": [        {            \"english_version\": \"An outbreak in DR Congo has been declared a health emergency, with almost 250 suspected cases reported. The agency said the outbreak, with around 246 cases and 80 deaths, does not meet the criteria of a pandemic emergency.\",            \"english_title\": \"Health Emergency in DR Congo\",            \"translated_version\": \"Un brote en RD Congo ha sido declarado emergencia de salud, con casi 250 casos sospechosos reportados. La agencia dijo que el brote, con alrededor de 246 casos y 80 muertes, no cumple con los criterios de emergencia pand\u00e9mica.\",            \"translated_title\": \"Emergencia de Salud en RD Congo\"        },        {            \"english_version\": \"BBC Verify has looked at many videos of fibre-optic drone attacks done by the Lebanese armed group.\",            \"english_title\": \"Drone Attacks by Lebanese Group\",            \"translated_version\": \"BBC Verify ha visto muchos videos de ataques con drones de fibra \u00f3ptica hechos por el grupo armado liban\u00e9s.\",            \"translated_title\": \"Ataques con Drones por Grupo Liban\u00e9s\"        },        {            \"english_version\": \"After his meeting in Beijing, the US president warned against Taiwan declaring independence.\",            \"english_title\": \"US President Warns on Taiwan\",            \"translated_version\": \"Despu\u00e9s de su reuni\u00f3n en Beijing, el presidente de EE.UU. advirti\u00f3 contra que Taiw\u00e1n declare independencia.\",            \"translated_title\": \"Presidente de EE.UU. Advierte sobre Taiw\u00e1n\"        },        {            \"english_version\": \"Ukraine's president says their strikes are a fair response to deadly Russian attacks on Ukrainian cities. The country is looking into where the strike came from, calling it a dangerous escalation.\",            \"english_title\": \"Ukraine Responds to Russian Attacks\",            \"translated_version\": \"El presidente de Ucrania dice que sus ataques son una respuesta justa a los ataques mortales rusos en ciudades ucranianas. El pa\u00eds est\u00e1 investigando de d\u00f3nde vino el ataque, llam\u00e1ndolo una escalada peligrosa.\",            \"translated_title\": \"Ucrania Responde a Ataques Rusos\"        },        {            \"english_version\": \"Eight people were hurt, four seriously, before people nearby chased and stopped the man.\",            \"english_title\": \"Man Stopped After Hurting People\",            \"translated_version\": \"Ocho personas resultaron heridas, cuatro de gravedad, antes de que personas cercanas persiguieran y detuvieran al hombre.\",            \"translated_title\": \"Hombre Detenido Tras Herir a Personas\"        }    ]}"